<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="step-n">step <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /step/    美 /step/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>脚步；步：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>walk with slow steps
慢步行走</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That’s one small step for a man, one giant leap for mankind.
对于一个人来说，这只是一小步。但对人类来说，这却是巨大的一步。</p><footer>——阿姆斯特朗</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>脚步声；脚印：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I know his steps.
我听得出他的脚步声。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I saw his steps in the snow.
我看见雪地上有他的脚印。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>阶梯；台阶：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a flight of 30 steps
一段30级的台阶</p></div>

<p>注: steps 常指室外的台阶，stairs 常指屋内的楼梯。  </p>
<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>步骤；措施：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>take a</strong> decisive / positive <strong>step</strong>
采取果断的/积极的措施</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This is the <strong>first step in</strong> reforming the welfare system.
这是福利制度改革的第一步。</p><footer>2012 辽宁</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In a word, Asian governments must <strong>take steps</strong> to improve the present situation as soon as possible.
总之，亚洲各国政府一定要尽快采取措施改善现状。</p><footer>2008 安徽</footer></div>

<h4 id="5-stage">5.★ <strong>阶段 (stage)；进程；等级 ：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Record your result, and go on to step 3.
把你的成绩记录下来，接着进入第三级。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You can start exercising slowly, and then increase the amount of exercise <strong>step by step</strong>.
开始锻炼的时候你可以慢点，然后逐步加大运动量。</p><footer>2009 湖南改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="mind-watch-ones-step">mind / watch one’s step</h3>
<p>1.<strong>走路小心；言行小心谨慎</strong>  </p></div>